title: Coast to Coast AM - 05-29-10 - Planets & Space News
description:
Date:
 05-29-10
 
Host:
 Ian Punnett
 
Guests:
 Neil deGrasse Tyson 
 


Ian Punnett was joined by astrophysicist and director of New York's Hayden Planetarium, Neil deGrasse Tyson, who discussed the once-yearly solar event known as "Manhattanhenge," as well as the latest news on space and planets.
